==English==

===Transitive verb===
'''to surround'''  ([[surrounds]], [[surrounded]], [[surrounding]])

#To [[encircle]] or [[simultaneously]] [[extend]] on all [[sides]] of something.
#To [[enclose]] or [[confine]] something on all sides so as to prevent [[escape]].

